6. Roadmap 2026-2028

Phase 1: Quanthos Core (Q2-Q4 2026)

· Formal language specification
· Basic compiler with QASM backend
· Integrated quantum simulator
· Documentation and tutorials

Phase 2: Quanthos Pro (2027)

· Complete Quanthos Studio IDE
· Multi-hardware support (superconducting, ions, photons)
· Advanced standard libraries
· Cloud integration (Azure Quantum, AWS Braket, IBM Cloud)

Phase 3: Quanthos Enterprise (2028)

· Formal verification tools
· Critical application certification
· Industrial partner ecosystem
· Developer training and certification

